:

1. *Niz* oluje je oborio stabla širom zemlje. (A series of storms knocked down trees across the country.)
2. Uspešno smo završili *niz* obaveza. (We successfully completed a series of duties.)
3. *Nizali* su se dan za danom. (They followed one after the other day by day.)
4. Nema potrebe da se *nizamo* po stepenicama. (There is no need to walk down the stairs one by one.)
5. Oni su se *nizali* u koloni. (They lined up in a column.)